{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762168542834","path":null,"data":{"id":4607,"title":"AIA:推出AIA自願醫保睿選計劃及「睿選明珠」醫療計劃","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1761045800243,"tags":["友邦保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">致合作夥伴:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; AIA於<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\">2025年10月27日(即首個保單申請日)</span></strong>推出<span style=\"color: #e71246;\"><strong>AIA自願醫保睿選計劃</strong></span>，此自願醫保靈活計劃將<strong>根據住院地區及所選的醫療服務</strong>提供者而<strong>提供普通房、半私家房以至標準私家房</strong>的不同級別住院保障。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 同時亦推出<strong>明珠版本<span style=\"color: #e71246;\">「睿選明珠」醫療計劃</span></strong>，為不同客戶提供貼心的醫療保障，助力應對人生各種重大事件。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 計劃<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>均不設分項賠償限額</strong></span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 一、產品特點:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-10-21/mceclip14_5cf4ab0713614c89b60de33b4dcb1580.png\" width=\"400\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>二、健康增值服務:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; AIA提供升級的<strong>保險業首創<span style=\"color: #e71246;\">「全助你」服務</span></strong>，<strong>新增兩項貼心特點</strong>，全面照顧客戶在中國內地的健康流程。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>1.中國內地一對一健康管家禮賓服務</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-10-21/mceclip15_6786088ab73348df8eb0794cbb6ca984.png\" width=\"400\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-10-21/mceclip16_0650600336bf493ba0155f38ac27e96b.png\" width=\"400\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-10-21/mceclip18_773137c6445e47e9aaec0c3400ebca4c.png\" width=\"400\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>2.[升級]AIA+尋找及預約網絡醫生功能</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 為協助客戶<strong>選擇「睿選指定醫院」及預約網絡醫生</strong>，客戶可透過<strong><span style=\"color: #e71246;\">AIA+的尋找及預約網絡醫生功能</span></strong>輕鬆篩選心儀的專科、醫生及醫院，並使用保險業首創<strong><span style=\"color: #e71246;\">即時網上預約功能</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"推出AIA自願醫保睿選計劃及「睿選明珠」醫療計劃_TC&EN.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2025-10-21/推出AIA自願醫保睿選計劃及「睿選明珠」醫療計劃_TC&EN_cf018047ed9b41d1818b45ac82e4dfb1.pdf","uploadTime":1761044064356,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"產品資料冊_TC.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2025-10-21/產品資料冊_TC_5e08cc838deb4ddf84220249e89ed261.pdf","uploadTime":1761044068600,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"產品資料冊_EN.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2025-10-21/產品資料冊_EN_b030b7ea8da74173aea2cf1eb1a6b38e.pdf","uploadTime":1761044072422,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"AIA","companyName":"友邦保險","productCodes":["AIA:AVSW","AIA:SWP"],"productNames":["AIA自願醫保睿選計劃","睿選明珠醫療計劃"],"companyCodes":["AIA"],"companyNames":["友邦保險"],"startEffectiveDate":1761555995621,"endEffectiveDate":null,"effective":true}}